{"word":"G5512 - χλευάζω - chleuázō - khlyoo-ad'-zo - Mock","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χλευάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chleuázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khlyoo-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Mock</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பரியாசம்"},{"paragraph":"to deride, mock, jeer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative probably of <a href=\"#/G5491 - χεῖλος - cheîlos - khi'-los/5491\">G5491</a>; to <i>throw out</i> the <i>lip</i>, that is, <i>jeer</i> at: - mock.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}